    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person! I have babied this car since day one, and it is in absolutely pristine, mint condition. It looks and smells just like it did when it first left the showroom\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and has been kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage. I'm looking for a quick sale to a good home, so come grab this gem before someone else does! \u2728",
