      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Offered is a concourse-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and a recently overhauled VANOS system utilizing Beisan Systems components. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a 3.62 limited-slip rear differential. The chassis is impeccably maintained, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension refresh with Bilstein B16 PSS10 coilovers for optimized damping and rebound. No deferred maintenance; the cooling system, including the expansion tank and water pump, has been proactively replaced. Riding on staggered Style 67 forged wheels wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber. This is a collector-quality specimen for the discerning purist seeking mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
